#

Lemon Herb Shrimp and Avocado Soup

$12.99
320 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodSoupHealthy

Description

A refreshing and zesty shrimp soup with creamy avocado and a hint of lemon, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Avocado: 2 ripe
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Red pepper flakes: 1/2 tsp
